OL,4,CCanada mourns as remains of 215
OL,5,Cchildren found at indigenous school
OL,6, A mass grave containing the remains of
OL,7, 215 children has been found in Canada
OL,8, at a former residential school set up
OL,9, to assimilate indigenous people.
OL,11,FThe children were students at the
OL,12,FKamloops Indian Residential School in
OL,13,FBritish Columbia that closed in 1978.
OL,15,FThe discovery was announced on Thursday
OL,16,Fby the chief of the Tk'emlups te
OL,17,FSecwepemc First Nation.
OL,19,FPrime Minister Justin Trudeau said it
OL,20,Fwas a "painful reminder" of a "shameful
OL,21,Fchapter of our country's history".
